      {
        "type": "narrative",
        "heading": "German Tourist Numbers Soar",
        "body": "In the chart below, you can see how the number of German cruise passengers rises sharply over the years, especially after 2010. Starting from around 12,700 in 2002, it soars to almost 49,000 by 2019. This suggests a growing interest in Iceland among German tourists.",
