      },
      {
        "type": "narrative",
        "heading": "Dutch Visitors Dip After a Peak",
        "body": "The number of Dutch cruise passengers shows a more varied story. In the chart below, you see an initial climb to a peak of about 1,415 in 2008. However, following this peak, the numbers decline to around 1,200 by 2019. This dip highlights fluctuations in interest over the years.",
