      },
      {
        "type": "narrative",
        "heading": "What This Means for Residents",
        "body": "These trends reflect not only changing travel patterns but also opportunities. The surge in German tourists, for example, might mean more German-language services and businesses in the city. For city residents, this could lead to new economic benefits and cultural exchanges."
